<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> vīrapāṇṭiya tEvaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="29">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 9</num> ceya
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ciñka kulakālavaḷanāṭṭuṉ paṉaṅkāṭṭu nāṭṭup peruṅkōḷū
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rāka Icainta Ūravaṟku teṉmalaināṭṭu vattaṇṭār kō
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭṭai Araiyakaḷil vattaṇṭār tēvaṉāṉa naraiñat tēva
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṉu mivaṉ tampi kaṟuppāṇṭāṉu miviruvarōm Ācaṟiya
<lb n="6" break="no"/>piramāṇam paṇṇikkuṭutta paricāvatu Iṉāḷ mutal ca
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ntirātittavarai Eṅkaḷai kāttu nōkkip pōtak ka
<lb n="8" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> vum nōkkumiṭattu nāṅkaḷum Āṇṭoṉ
<lb n="9"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> nellaḷakka kaṭavōmākavum Innellu
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> Eṅkaḷai maṟiccukkuṭuttum koḷḷakkaṭavarā
<lb n="11"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> Ippaṭi cammatittu Āciṟiya piramāṇam paṇṇi
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="11" unit="character"/> 
</p>

